				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This one-liner triggers just after players attack Father Carrion. He reacts to the way in which the combat was triggered - if the player destroyed his heart he is furious, because his means of resurrecting is gone. In other instances, he knows his death will not be permanent and is more confident."
				}
